{"tid":295228,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[嚇到瀨屎] 緊急封尖咀鐘樓維修　政府拒絕民族黨「悼念淪陷20年」集會申請","createTime":"2017-06-23T14:45:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T03:58:11.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"14f197b2d1bd6433d30ab56ee2ec733b7ce5d288","tid":295228,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:45:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170623/photo/bkn-20170623132722765-0623_00822_001_01b.jpg?20170623134427\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170623%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170623132722765-0623_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20170623134427&h=32fcdb5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主張「港獨」的香港民族黨，日前宣布擬於本月30日晚上，在尖沙咀文化中心外舉行「悼念香港淪陷20年」集會。民族黨召集人陳浩天今早在其個人Facebook上表示，收到警方的通知，指康文署將於當日封閉文化中心鐘樓附近作維修，因此民族黨未能舉行集會。<br />\n<br />\n陳浩天在其貼文上留言反問，指「唔係要我地(哋)參加其他慶祝活動下(吓)嘛」，亦回應網民指警方稱無辦法提議其他可舉行集會的地點。他回覆東網查詢時表示，暫時未有其他安排。<br />\n<br />\n民族黨早前指，該黨將舉辦的集會是和平晚會，當中會有分享、悼念、播放影片等環節，完結後不會有其他行動。陳浩天日前亦向警方申請不反對通知書，預料300人出席。"},{"pid":"df493162d57baaa25e2e0e7f215ce8a3a29cb8dc","tid":295228,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:45:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4de76fc4f78edc4e34a99b227e96b2df09775d64","tid":295228,"uid":61488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:47:26.000Z","msg":"去返添馬公園今天我lo"},{"pid":"8d62e7e123ae361e52c778eabb04f0c219f8c7ad","tid":295228,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:52:32.000Z","msg":"學中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前學額分配有問題 成班家長諗住去示威<br />\n跟住就政府門口修路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4716367d73efdf3a32c5799c54b84b377bec16","tid":295228,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:57:43.000Z","msg":"On撚9"},{"pid":"7f859c318e82fd854ff5c66a2a7fc5e8a9540dbd","tid":295228,"uid":36115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T15:01:34.000Z","msg":"本身都係預計300人出席咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0238cc342927e82e25c08ffcb6447ff621c93f31","tid":295228,"uid":98692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T15:02:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">預料300人出席</span><br />\n最後會唔會得30個？你知鍵盤戰士從來唔出黎"},{"pid":"15387e299f9b97b5e96e46752a3e83696ff8d175","tid":295228,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T15:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170623/s00001/5339a0c0f0c58984b358275b0daa407a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170623%2Fs00001%2F5339a0c0f0c58984b358275b0daa407a.jpg&h=1843cceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170623/s00001/1498202421083\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170623%2Fs00001%2F1498202421083&d=9wh4JD1edWobAJGetJbuDQEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=950a3ad2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170623%2Fs00001%2F1498202421083&h=1384bdb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170623/s00001/1498202421083</a><br />\n<br />\n香港民族黨召集人陳浩天擬於6月30日即回歸20周年前夕在尖沙嘴鐘樓舉行集會，惟他今日在其facebook指，獲通知康文署將在當晚全封上址以作「維修活動」，導致他未能舉行集會，《明報》下午前往現場了解，發現大量鐵馬，部分地方貼上告示指需要維修，但仍可自由出入。<br />\n<br />\n康文署回覆本報查詢時表示，為配合回歸20周年的大型煙花匯演活動，文化中心廣場設施的維修和清潔工作必須於6月30日上午9時至7月1日上午11時進行，以趕及市民在晚上於該處觀賞煙花。而7月1日當天的日間時段，廣場已出租予舉辦活動。<br />\n<br />\n《明報》下午到尖沙嘴鐘樓一帶了解，管理員及清楚工人表示對6月30日晚上全封一事不知情，未見有關於全封告示，惟見到有大量鐵馬，部分地上擺放鐵馬，並貼上告示︰「維修工程進行中，暫停使用」，但不見有工程人員進行維修。<br />\n<br />\n倡議「港獨」的香港民族黨召集人陳浩天日前透露，6月30日即回歸20周年前夕，將在尖沙嘴鐘樓舉行和平集會「悼念香港淪陷20年」，但陳今日在其facebook更新情況，指接獲警方通知康文署轄下的文化中心附近鐘樓將在當晚全封以作「維修活動」。"},{"pid":"2cba98fb03d27c20c78083268097557a50bd4993","tid":295228,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T15:51:47.000Z","msg":"垃圾政府"},{"pid":"b67d25c1be7b022bbc07e55e4f8de30d4e444af3","tid":295228,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T16:16:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>轉場咪得<br />\n或者再對出</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n'指警方稱無辦法提議其他可舉行集會的地點。'<br />\n<br />\n嗰幾日全港冇地方可以集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8290a587a63d79e8f88d7a24f459fc459f502277","tid":295228,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T16:21:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>轉場咪得<br />\n或者再對出</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n'指警方稱無辦法提議其他可舉行集會的地點。'<br />\n<br />\n嗰幾日全港冇地方可以集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去習總果間酒店樓下呢??<br />\n<br />\n最危險地方係最安全既地方"},{"pid":"c92e0c9eb0a40be5749094f62062d44a11556c26","tid":295228,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T16:26:29.000Z","msg":"封哂成個尖沙咀囉"},{"pid":"261def25539146507bcab53ec06abb7942f4f685","tid":295228,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T03:53:16.000Z","msg":"突發"},{"pid":"5bdd63f573069ee53807740718e86979bacca6e6","tid":295228,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T03:55:14.000Z","msg":"123"},{"pid":"143eae6c9543419e4d3cbcbdc411d3aa70e71639","tid":295228,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:25:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">預料300人出席<